	   <tr><td colspan=2>In response to the three previous posts:-<br><br>1) The PH is the only standing Putrid Skeleton in the undead ruins in South Karana - these ruins are south and slightly west of the bridge to NK.<br><br>2) It is possible for a Dark Elf Cleric to obtain this item (I am one and I did).&nbsp;&nbsp;However you will need to do a large amount of faction work.  It took me many hours to achieve Ally faction with the Priests of Life.<br><br>There is another rare spawn in these ruins, which is Ghanex Drah (a named undead gnoll) for the monk red headband quest.  This quest is a pre-requisite for the monk epic.  If Ghanex Drah spawns, kill him - he may drop a head which is greatly desired by monks.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
